overview: Welcome to ANOTHER edition of "Lost & Found Video Night"! We are back with vol. 22! That's right, vol. 22!! Prepare for movie weirdness from around the world, public access conspiracy wackos, a deep dive into "Elvis is alive" sightings, rare commercials, Andy Kaufman wrestling women, music from The Dead Kennedys, The Geto Boys, Willie Nelson, The Metamatics & more, more, more!
title: Lost & Found Video Night Vol. 22
